settings.html:
<style>

    .gallery-icon,
    .gallery-item{
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
    }
    .elementor-image-gallery .gallery-item img {
        transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
        width: 100%;
        height: 500px;
        object-fit: cover;
    }
    .elementor-image-gallery .gallery-item:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.08);
        
    }
    
    .elementor-image-gallery .gallery-item:hover .gallery-icon::before {
        content: '';
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--e-global-color-mac-custom-7-color) 0%, var(--e-global-color-primary) 100%) !important;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: 1;
        
        
        
    }
    
    @media(max-width: 1024px) {
        .elementor-image-gallery .gallery-item img {
            height: 350px;
        }
    }
     @media(min-width: 400px) {
        .elementor-image-gallery .gallery-item {
            width: 50% !important;
            
        }   
     }
    
    @media(max-width: 400px) {

        .elementor-image-gallery .gallery-item {
            width: 100% !important;
            
        }
        .elementor-image-gallery .gallery-item img {
            height: 350px;
        }
    }

/*-------------------------------------------------------*/

     .jet-testimonials__content{
        padding: 20px 25px;
    }
    
/*-------------------------------------------------------*/
.custom-gallery .swiper-slide-inner {
    height: 300px !important;
}
.custom-gallery img{
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 300px;
    border-radius: 20px;
}
    
    
    
</style>
